        %p I studied software engineering in Cyprus, and, inspired by computers and technology, moved to the US in 2008. In order to establish myself here, I went into marketing, sales, and management.
        %p In my 4 years at Verizon Wireless, I trained Store Managers and Sales Specialists for over 15 stores and became Best Manager of the Year. We surpassed revenue-per-sale goals by over 20% and 5 of my trainees went on to get promotions (4 of which were in management).
