        %p Eventually, I found my way to Dev Bootcamp, where I learned how to be a more productive and efficient software engineer. As a software developer, I love the feeling of being confused, knowing that the very next thing is a better understanding of that topic or language. I am strongly focused on usability, functionality, code quality and design.
        %p My interests and specialties include: Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, CSS, Sass, Bootstrap, Materialize, SQL, Swift (Beginner), Python (Beginner), Angular.JS and MEAN Stack (Beginner).
        %p
